    <h3>Concurrent Editing Protection</h3>
    <p>
        Using <strong>Redis locks</strong>, the application prevents concurrent editing of the same user profile.
        This mechanism ensures data integrity and avoids conflicting changes:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Locks are automatically acquired when a user starts editing.</li>
        <li>Locks expire after 30 seconds unless renewed.</li>
        <li>Only clients holding the lock can save changes.</li>
        <li>Locks are released after saving or canceling the edit.</li>
    </ul>

